i-item-spacing\">Chapter Chronology</caption>\n\t\n\t<tbody>\n\t<tr>\n\t\n\t\t<td class=\"pi-horizontal-group-item pi-data-value pi-font pi-border-color pi-item-spacing\">← <a href=\"/wiki/Chapter_119\" title=\"Chapter 119\">Previous</a></td>\n\t\n\t\t<td class=\"pi-horizontal-group-item pi-data-value pi-font pi-border-color pi-item-spacing\"><a href=\"/wiki/Chapter_121\" title=\"Chapter 121\">Next</a> →</td>\n\t\n\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n\n</section>\n</aside>\n\n<b>Chapter 120</b> is titled \"The Red Ogre Cried\".\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\" role=\"navigation\" aria-labelledby=\"mw-toc-heading\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2 id=\"mw-toc-heading\">Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Cover_Page\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Cover Page</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Short_Summary\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Short Summary</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Long_Summary\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Long Summary</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Quick_Reference\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quick Reference</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Chapter_Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Chapter Notes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Characters\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Characters</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Author_Comment\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Author Comment</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#Trivia\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Trivia</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#Site_Navigation\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">7</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Site Navigation</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Cover_Page\">Cover Page</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_120%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D1&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/wiki/Cover_Page#Animal_Theater\" title=\"Cover Page\">Animal Theater</a>: <a href=\"/wiki/Monkey_D._Luffy\" title=\"Monkey D. Luffy\">Luffy</a> cross a scrubland on camelback. He has lent his hat to the camel, with a cobra taking its place on his own head; all three hang their tongues identically in the blistering heat.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Short_Summary\">Short Summary</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_120%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D2&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/wiki/Brogy\" title=\"Brogy\">Brogy</a> defeats <a href=\"/wiki/Dorry\" title=\"Dorry\">Dorry</a> thanks to <a href=\"/wiki/Galdino\" title=\"Galdino\">Mr. 3</a>'s interference, but Mr. 3 then comes in and overwhelms Brogy by using the power of the <a href=\"/wiki/Doru_Doru_no_Mi\" title=\"Doru Doru no Mi\">Doru Doru no Mi</a> to cover his body in wax. Meanwhile, <a href=\"/wiki/Gem\" title=\"Gem\">Mr. 5</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/Mikita\" title=\"Mikita\">Miss Valentine</a> confront <a href=\"/wiki/Monkey_D._Luffy\" title=\"Monkey D. Luffy\">Luffy</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/Usopp\" title=\"Usopp\">Usopp</a>, and <a href=\"/wiki/Nefertari_Vivi\" title=\"Nefertari Vivi\">Vivi</a> after defeating <a href=\"/wiki/Karoo\" title=\"Karoo\">Karoo</a>, and they capture Vivi to bring her to Mr. 3.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Long_Summary\">Long Summary</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_120%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D3&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/wiki/Galdino\" title=\"Galdino\">Mr. 3</a>'s interference allows <a href=\"/wiki/Brogy\" title=\"Brogy\">Brogy</a> to land a great blow on <a href=\"/wiki/Dorry\" title=\"Dorry\">Dorry</a>'s chest, defeating the latter. <a href=\"/wiki/Monkey_D._Luffy\" title=\"Monkey D. Luffy\">Luffy</a> becomes very enraged and yells out, wanting to know who had weakened Dorry. <a href=\"/wiki/Marianne\" title=\"Marianne\">Miss Goldenweek</a> hears him, but Mr. 3 pays no attention. Brogy starts to cry with happiness over finally winning in their duel, when Mr. 3 approaches him and thanks him. He introduces himself to Brogy before revealing that he has encased the giant's feet with wax using the power of the <a href=\"/wiki/Doru_Doru_no_Mi\" title=\"Doru Doru no Mi\">Doru Doru no Mi</a>.\n</p><p>Meanwhile, <a href=\"/wiki/Usopp\" title=\"Usopp\">Usopp</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/Nefertari_Vivi\" title=\"Nefertari Vivi\">Vivi</a> decide to go find the people who harmed Dorry. Right then, however, <a href=\"/wiki/Gem\" title=\"Gem\">Mr. 5</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/Mikita\" title=\"Mikita\">Miss Valentine</a> come out of the woods with a defeated <a href=\"/wiki/Karoo\" title=\"Karoo\">Karoo</a>. Mr. 5 reveals that they had been trying to lure Vivi away from Luffy by forcing Karoo to cry out for her, but the duck refused even to the point of severe beating. Usopp asks if they put the bomb in Dorry's rum, which they affirm, and they note that they had not seen him before. Usopp and Vivi then pull out their weapons and race to attack, with Usopp launching an explosive shot at Mr. 5. However, Mr. 5 is unharmed due to his <a href=\"/wiki/Bomu_Bomu_no_Mi\" title=\"Bomu Bomu no Mi\">Devil Fruit power</a>, and he responds by flicking an explosive ball of mucus at Usopp. Miss Valentine then leaps into the air before <a href=\"/wiki/Kiro_Kiro_no_Mi\" title=\"Kiro Kiro no Mi\">becoming much heavier</a> and slamming into Usopp. Vivi attempts to attack Mr. 5, but he overwhelms her with an explosion before grabbing her by the neck. He says that he is not going to kill Vivi, but rather take her to Mr. 3 on his orders. Meanwhile, Mr. 3 has pinned Brogy to the ground with his wax as he states his intention to create a masterpiece of artwork.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quick_Reference\">Quick Reference</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_120%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D4&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Chapter_Notes\">Chapter Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_120%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D5&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Brogy\" title=\"Brogy\">Brogy</a> defeats <a href=\"/wiki/Dorry\" title=\"Dorry\">Dorry</a> due to <a href=\"/wiki/Baroque_Works\" title=\"Baroque Works\">Baroque Works</a>' interference.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Usopp\" title=\"Usopp\">Usopp</a> meets <a href=\"/wiki/Gem\" title=\"Gem\">Mr. 5</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/Mikita\" title=\"Mikita\">Miss Valentine</a> for the first time, and the two Officer Agents quickly realize that he is a member of Luffy's crew.</li>\n<li>Mr. 5 and Miss Valentine capture Vivi to bring her to Mr. 3.</li>\n<li>Mr. 3 captures Brogy and states his intention to create a piece of art.</li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Characters\">Characters</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_120%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D6&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<table class=\"CharTable\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th><a href=\"/wiki/Pirate\" title=\"Pirate\">Pirates</a>\n</th>\n<th>Citizens\n</th>\n<th><a href=\"/wiki/Baroque_Works\" title=\"Baroque Works\">Baroque Works</a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<dl><dt><a href=\"/wiki/Straw_Hat_Pirates\" title=\"Straw Hat Pirates\">Straw Hat Pirates</a></dt></dl>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Monkey_D._Luffy\" title=\"Monkey D. Luffy\">Monkey D. Luffy</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Usopp\" title=\"Usopp\">Usopp</a></li></ul>\n</td>\n<td>\n<dl><dt><a href=\"/wiki/Little_Garden\" title=\"Little Garden\">Little Garden</a></dt></dl>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Dorry\" title=\"Dorry\">Dorry</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Brogy\" title=\"Brogy\">Brogy</a></li></ul>\n<hr />\n<dl><dt><a href=\"/wiki/Arabasta\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Arabasta\">Arabasta</a></dt></dl>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Nefertari_Vivi\" title=\"Nefertari Vivi\">Nefertari Vivi</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Karoo\" title=\"Karoo\">Karoo</a></li></ul>\n</td>\n<td>\n<dl><dt><a href=\"/wiki/Baroque_Works#Members\" title=\"Baroque Works\">Officer Agents</a></dt></dl>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Galdino\" title=\"Galdino\">Mr. 3</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Marianne\" title=\"Marianne\">Miss Goldenweek</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Gem\" title=\"Gem\">Mr. 5</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Mikita\" title=\"Mikita\">Miss Valentine</a></li></ul>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Author_Comment\">Author Comment</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_120%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D7&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><br />\n</p><table class=\"wikitable\" style=\"margin: auto; text-align: center; width:50%\">\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/wiki/List_of_WSJ_Author_Comments\" title=\"List of WSJ Author Comments\">Author Comment</a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:90%\"><div class=\"tabber wds-tabber\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__wrapper with-bottom-border\"><ul class=\"wds-tabs\"><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab wds-is-current\" data-hash=\"Translation\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">Translation</a></div></li><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab\" data-hash=\"Original\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">Original</a></div></li></ul></div><div class=\"wds-tab__content wds-is-current\"><p><br />\nI bought a hybrid cell phone. I'm always in the house but I just wanted one darnit!!</p></div><div class=\"wds-tab__content\"><p><br />\nハイブリッドケータイを買った。そりゃずっと家（ウチ）にゃいるけど、欲しかったんだ――!!</p></div></div>—<a href=\"/wiki/Eiichiro_Oda\" title=\"Eiichiro Oda\">Eiichiro Oda</a></td><td><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/Eiichiro_Oda\" title=\"Eiichiro Oda\"><img src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/onepiece/images/a/ad/Eiichiro_Oda_WSJ_Avatar.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/100?cb=20230801133230\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" class=\"mw-file-element\" data-image-name=\"Eiichiro Oda WSJ Avatar.png\" data-image-key=\"Eiichiro_Oda_WSJ_Avatar.png\" data-relevant=\"1\" /></a></span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"><i>English translation by <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.thegrandline.com/odatocLIVE.htm\">Greg Werner</a>. For comprehensive translation credits, see <a href=\"/wiki/List_of_WSJ_Author_Comments#Translation_Credits\" title=\"List of WSJ Author Comments\">here</a>.</i></td></tr>\n\n</tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Trivia\">Trivia</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_120%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D8&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>This chapter's title is a reference to <i><a href=\"https://c2.com/cgi/wiki?ja:%E6%B3%A3%E3%81%84%E3%81%9F%E8%B5%A4%E9%AC%BC\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"wiki:ja:泣いた赤鬼\">The Crying Red Ogre</a></i><span style=\"font-weight: normal\"> (<span class=\"t_nihongo_kanji\" lang=\"ja\">泣いた赤鬼</span><span class=\"t_nihongo_comma\">,</span> <i><span class=\"t_nihongo_romaji\">Naita aka-oni</span></i><span class=\"t_nihongo_help\"><sup><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Help:Japanese\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"wikipedia:Help:Japanese\"><span class=\"t_nihongo_icon\" style=\"color:#00e;font:bold 80% sans-serif;text-decoration:none;padding:0 .1em;\">?</span></a></sup></span>)</span>, a classic Japanese picture-book by Hirosuke Hamada.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Site_Navigation\">Site Navigation</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_120%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D9&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"