    "wikitext": {
      "*": "{{Chapter Box\n| title = The Red Ogre Cried\n| image = \n| jname = 赤鬼が泣いた\n| rname = Akaoni ga Naita\n| ename = The Red Ogre Weeps\n}}\n'''Chapter 120''' is titled \"The Red Ogre Cried\".\n\n==Cover Page==\n[[Cover Page#Animal Theater|Animal Theater]]: [[Monkey D. Luffy|Luffy]] cross a scrubland on camelback. He has lent his hat to the camel, with a cobra taking its place on his own head; all three hang their tongues identically in the blistering heat.\n\n==Short Summary==\n[[Brogy]] defeats [[Dorry]] thanks to [[Galdino|Mr. 3]]'s interference, but Mr. 3 then comes in and overwhelms Brogy by using the power of the [[Doru Doru no Mi]] to cover his body in wax. Meanwhile, [[Gem|Mr. 5]] and [[Mikita|Miss Valentine]] confront [[Monkey D. Luffy|Luffy]], [[Usopp]], and [[Nefertari Vivi|Vivi]] after defeating [[Karoo]], and they capture Vivi to bring her to Mr. 3.\n\n==Long Summary==\n[[Galdino|Mr. 3]]'s interference allows [[Brogy]] to land a great blow on [[Dorry]]'s chest, defeating the latter. [[Monkey D. Luffy|Luffy]] becomes very enraged and yells out, wanting to know who had weakened Dorry. [[Marianne|Miss Goldenweek]] hears him, but Mr. 3 pays no attention. Brogy starts to cry with happiness over finally winning in their duel, when Mr. 3 approaches him and thanks him. He introduces himself to Brogy before revealing that he has encased the giant's feet with wax using the power of the [[Doru Doru no Mi]].\n\nMeanwhile, [[Usopp]] and [[Nefertari Vivi|Vivi]] decide to go find the people who harmed Dorry. Right then, however, [[Gem|Mr. 5]] and [[Mikita|Miss Valentine]] come out of the woods with a defeated [[Karoo]]. Mr. 5 reveals that they had been trying to lure Vivi away from Luffy by forcing Karoo to cry out for her, but the duck refused even to the point of severe beating. Usopp asks if they put the bomb in Dorry's rum, which they affirm, and they note that they had not seen him before. Usopp and Vivi then pull out their weapons and race to attack, with Usopp launching an explosive shot at Mr. 5. However, Mr. 5 is unharmed due to his [[Bomu Bomu no Mi|Devil Fruit power]], and he responds by flicking an explosive ball of mucus at Usopp. Miss Valentine then leaps into the air before [[Kiro Kiro no Mi|becoming much heavier]] and slamming into Usopp. Vivi attempts to attack Mr. 5, but he overwhelms her with an explosion before grabbing her by the neck. He says that he is not going to kill Vivi, but rather take her to Mr. 3 on his orders. Meanwhile, Mr. 3 has pinned Brogy to the ground with his wax as he states his intention to create a masterpiece of artwork.\n\n==Quick Reference==\n===Chapter Notes===\n*[[Brogy]] defeats [[Dorry]] due to [[Baroque Works]]' interference.\n*[[Usopp]] meets [[Gem|Mr. 5]] and [[Mikita|Miss Valentine]] for the first time, and the two Officer Agents quickly realize that he is a member of Luffy's crew.\n*Mr. 5 and Miss Valentine capture Vivi to bring her to Mr. 3.\n*Mr. 3 captures Brogy and states his intention to create a piece of art.\n\n===Characters===\n{| class=\"CharTable\"\n! [[Pirate]]s\n! Citizens\n! [[Baroque Works]]\n|-\n|\n;[[Straw Hat Pirates]]\n*[[Monkey D. Luffy]]\n*[[Usopp]]\n|\n;[[Little Garden]]\n*[[Dorry]]\n*[[Brogy]]\n----\n;[[Arabasta]]\n*[[Nefertari Vivi]]\n*[[Karoo]]\n|\n;[[Baroque Works#Members|Officer Agents]]\n*[[Galdino|Mr. 3]]\n*[[Marianne|Miss Goldenweek]]\n*[[Gem|Mr. 5]]\n*[[Mikita|Miss Valentine]]\n|}\n\n==Author Comment==\n{{WSJ Comment}}\n\n==Trivia==\n*This chapter's title is a reference to {{nihongo|''[[wiki:ja:泣いた赤鬼|The Crying Red Ogre]]''|泣いた赤鬼|Naita aka-oni}}, a classic Japanese picture-book by Hirosuke Hamada.\n\n==Site Navigation==\n{{Little Garden Arc}}[[ca:Capítol 120]]\n[[it:Capitolo 120]]\n[[fr:Chapitre 120]]"
